transcribe-legacy: The Transcribe! application is an assistant for people who sometimes
transcribe-legacy: want to work out a piece of music from a recording, in order to
transcribe-legacy: write it out, or play it themselves, or both. It doesn't do the
transcribe-legacy: transcribing for you, but it is essentially a specialised player
transcribe-legacy: program which is optimised for the purpose of transcription. It
transcribe-legacy: has many transcription-specific features not found on conventional
transcribe-legacy: music players.
